.description
Phone-Line-Watcher.  For users of Hayes compatible modems.  Monitors the
serial port and records all incoming calls.  Allows a remote user to login,
receive and leave a message, and transfer files via Zmodem in either
direction.  Two level DOS access, Disabled DOS-requestors and more.
Greatly enhanced version of initial release on disk 363.  
